  <brief_title>Evaluation of Impaired Microcirculation During Septic Shock With Contrast Enhanced Ultrasound</brief_title>
  <official_title>Messung Von Mikrozirkulationsstörungen im Septischen Schock Mit Kontrastmittel- verstärkter Sonographie Evaluation of Impaired Microcirculation During Septic Shock With Contrast Enhanced Ultrasound</official_title>
